com.lucidworks.fusion.connector.plugin.api.fetcher.type.content

Interface MessageHelper

  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface MessageHelper
    FetchInput - can produce Documents, Candidates, Skips, Deletes, and Errors Document - a result of a FetchInput that will be indexed into the content collection. A single Document may be emitted, or multiple. For example, if a FetchInput is a CSV file, each row may end up as an emitted Document. The fetchInputId is always the Id of the FetchInput.

    Candidate - This type represents a yet to be fully validated "child" of the provided FetchInput. The parent of a Candidate is _always_ the FetchInput. Multiple Candidates can be emitted per FetchInput. The fetchInputId is always the Id of the FetchInput.
